pageContext.claim: “The African-Americans have the best employment numbers in the history of our country....I think if you look at the numbers for African-American unemployment, best numbers they've had- literally the best numbers they've had in history.”
pageContext.analysis: The African-American unemployment statistic has been in existence for less than 50 years. It reached a low of 5.9 percent in May 2018, but had risen to 6.8 percent by the time Trump made these remarks.
